      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver on a budget. The engine and transmission are operational, though there are some minor fluid leaks typical for its age and mileage that will require monitoring. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. It has been recently serviced for basic maintenance, but a prospective buyer should expect upcoming repairs to keep it in peak running order.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, making this an ideal choice for a collector or a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. It requires significant mechanical repairs and shows heavy wear on both the interior and exterior. Some systems are currently non-functional, and the body has visible damage.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
